comment: Zipser (CHI) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Joseph (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.

VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Rondo (CHI) maintains legal guarding position on Joseph's (TOR) drive to the basket and post up.
